## 5. Dependency Graph

```
index.ts
  ├── server/express.ts
  │     └── domain/usecases/{AnalyzeRepo, GetTrending}
  ├── server/mcp.ts
  │     └── domain/usecases/{AnalyzeRepo, GetTrending}
  ├── adapters/github/GithubAdapter.ts
  │     └── ports/RepoApiPort.ts   ← interface only
  └── adapters/database/PrismaAdapter.ts
        └── ports/MetricsRepoPort.ts  ← interface only

domain/usecases/AnalyzeRepo.ts
  ├── ports/RepoApiPort.ts     ← depends on interface, NOT GithubAdapter
  ├── ports/MetricsRepoPort.ts ← depends on interface, NOT PrismaAdapter
  └── domain/entities/Metrics.ts

domain/usecases/GetTrending.ts
  ├── ports/MetricsRepoPort.ts
  └── domain/entities/TrendingRepo.ts
```

**Dependency rule: arrows point inward. Domain knows nothing outside itself.**

