## 9. Key Architectural Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|----------|--------|-----------|
| HTTP framework | Express | Minimal overhead, ecosystem familiarity, easy middleware |
| ORM | Prisma | Type-safe queries, auto-generated client, migration tooling |
| GitHub client | Octokit | Official, handles auth, rate limits, pagination |
| MCP transport | stdio | Standard for local MCP servers, compatible with Claude Desktop |
| Caching strategy | DB upsert (last-write-wins) | Simple, queryable, 24h growth calculation built in |
| Dependency injection | Constructor injection | Explicit, testable, no DI container overhead needed at this scale |
| Port style | TypeScript interfaces | Zero runtime cost, pure contracts |

